node.text:
Three takeaways:
1. Fran is *never* “Friendly” 🤪
2. Run through the finish line before you sprawl out on the floor.
3. No matter how well you executed a workout, you’re always going to say you think you could’ve gone faster 🙃 That’s why we love CrossFit am I right- always improvements to be made 😈
•••
🎥: @jtwiseguy

node.text: Leaving Madison a little different than how I arrived. The emotions are a constant battle, but I’m still smiling & will keep you guys updated on this process. Love y’all 🤍

node.text: Tia, not only the greatest athlete of all time, but the greatest person of all time. She is truly such an inspiration, from witnessing the grit of hardest working individual in the world, & also the heart of the most caring & self-less friend. Congrats on your 5th CrossFit Games Title 🐐 I love ya 🤍

node.text:
Thank you for the overwhelming messages of support. 🙏🏼 There is no community like this and although I am heartbroken, I’m thriving off your energy and love. 🤍

Last night I dislocated my elbow during the max snatch event, and was forced to medically withdrawal.

I dedicated my life to being prepared for this years CrossFit Games and I’m absolutely the fittest I’ve ever been. To not be able to fight for a podium spot today crushes me, but I’ll be back. 

Thank you to the extremely professional medical staff that treated me on-site. This is a speedbump and it’s all part of my journey. Gods plan is bigger than mine. See you soon. 💓

node.text:
🔥 I AM OFFICIALLY BEAST MODE🔥

I’ve barely been able to keep this a secret! This week I’ve taken over the Beast Mode @Spotify playlist with @NOBULL. The Beast Mode playlist is the largest workout playlist on Spotify. To be the athlete featured as the thumbnail image, which hasn’t changed in YEARS, is an incredible feeling! 🤯 

Turn it UP during your training this week and post the playlist on your Instragram story tagging me and @NOBULL for a chance to win a free pair of my @CrossFitGames Trainers! #IAMNOBULL #Spotify #CrossFitGames
